621
00:46:03,697 --> 00:46:05,364
<i>The death of Irene Lester</i>

622
00:46:05,398 --> 00:46:07,109
<i>has sent shock waves
throughout the community.</i>

623
00:46:07,133 --> 00:46:09,670
