every day?!

658
00:48:55,735 --> 00:48:59,472
I go to sleep every night,
and I see her smiling face.

659
00:48:59,505 --> 00:49:03,108
I wake up thinking I'm gonna
see it again, only to realize

660
00:49:03,142 --> 00:49:06,345
