It's inappropriate.

696
00:52:22,108 --> 00:52:24,878
- Yeah, Daddy.
- Yeah.

697
00:52:24,911 --> 00:52:26,012
Whoa. Easy.

698
00:52:26,046 --> 00:52:28,213
- Oh!
- What are you doing?

699
00:52:28,247 --> 00:52:29,849
