725
00:56:58,116 --> 00:57:01,787
<i>Daniel...</i>

726
00:57:10,963 --> 00:57:13,632
<i>Daniel...</i>

727
00:57:38,323 --> 00:57:40,225
Hi, honey.

728
00:57:42,060 --> 00:57:44,363
