733
00:58:33,245 --> 00:58:36,715
Please sleep,
my baby darling girl.

734
00:59:09,181 --> 00:59:12,951
Aah!

735
00:59:18,657 --> 00:59:20,725
Oh, my God.

736
00:59:40,312 --> 00:59:42,414
