01:01:03,728 --> 01:01:05,530
for this whole thing
to blow over

755
01:01:05,565 --> 01:01:08,166
before the girls...
- Betty thought?

756
01:01:08,200 --> 01:01:10,068
W-What whole thing?

757
01:01:10,101 --> 01:01:14,540
Theresa, please don't do this.

758
01:01:14,574 --> 01:01:18,276
You have to admit that
Rosalie's...

