01:02:00,686 --> 01:02:02,655
Hello.

768
01:02:02,688 --> 01:02:04,322
Oh, evening, Detective.

769
01:02:06,592 --> 01:02:08,159
Oh.

770
01:02:10,462 --> 01:02:12,297
